          <p class="text-slate-200 p-text pb-5">A private pilot certificate is the place to start for those who have always dreamt of flying their own aircraft. This certificate allows you to operate an aircraft for non-commercial purposes.  Our expert instructors will guide you through the fundamentals of flight, teaching you how to take off, land, and navigate the skies with confidence.</p>
          <%#= link_to "PRIVATE PILOT TRAINING", private_pilot_path, class: "btn-primary bg-slate-500 hover:bg-slate-400 text-base" %>
        </div>

        <div class="col-start-5 col-end-6 md:mx-auto hidden md:block relative mr-10">
          <div class="h-full w-6 flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="h-full w-0.5 bg-ideal-blue pointer-events-none"></div>
          </div>

          <div class="w-6 h-6 absolute top-1/2 -mt-3 border-2 border-ideal-blue rounded-full bg-ideal-blue shadow"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex md:contents">
        <div class="col-start-5 col-end-6 mr-10 md:mx-auto hidden md:block relative">
