          <h3 class="font-semibold text-xl mb-1 text-white">Instrument Rating</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-200 p-text pb-5">Take your flying to the next level. An Instrument Rating equips you with the knowledge and skills to fly in low visibility and adverse weather conditions using only your aircraft's instruments. This rating opens up a whole new world of possibilities, making you a safer and more proficient pilot.</p>
          <%#= link_to "INSTRUMENT TRAINING", root_path, class: "btn-primary bg-slate-500 hover:bg-slate-400 text-base" %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-row-reverse md:contents">
        <div class="w-full col-start-1 col-end-5 p-4 rounded-xl my-4 ml-auto bg-ideal-blue">
