          <p class="text-slate-200 p-text pb-5">A commercial certificate allows you to fly for compensation or hire.  Our experienced instructors will help you master the skills needed to operate advanced aircraft, including advanced maneuvers and emergency procedures, ensuring that you are fully equipped for the challenges that lie ahead.</p>
          <%#= link_to "COMMERCIAL TRAINING", root_path, class: "btn-primary bg-slate-500 hover:bg-slate-400 text-base" %>
        </div>

        <div class="col-start-5 col-end-6 md:mx-auto hidden md:block relative mr-10">
